sources.title: Manfish
sources.description: Lon Chaney. Victor Jory and John Bromfield star in this nautically set variation on the Poe stories The Tell-Tale Heart and The Gold Bug. Three fishermen go in search of a treasure and it leads to murder.

sources.title: Manfish
sources.description: Three deep sea divers get involved in murder while searching for a lost treasure.
